title: #LiveOutside SF Episode 11: Mural Unveiling
description:
This is the moment when it all comes together. After 9 long days of painting in the rain and through many nights, Alynn-Mags party with friends and Painted Palms to celebrate the final mural unveiling. #JanSport #LiveOutside 

Music: "Forever" PAINTED PALMS
